column3: Built NEW.  Installed NEW Iridium SIM Card.
Successfully tested all MET sensor inputs, IM data, and GPS. RF Modem not working with 1st time install of v2.01, 170530 firmware
RF modem working with version 1.12, 150313 firmware.  Then still working when upgrading to v2.01, 170530
Ran Bench current drain test for 3 days with version 2.01, 170530 firmware, RF modem turned off, 13.64mA Average.
Tested internal Iridium antenna by doing an XMIT outside, which successfully registered and sent dummy files.
Back from Indonesia, IO1-18, NOT deployed, needs checkout/upgrades.
Installed metal SS standoffs on bottom of circuit board stack.
Ran Bench current drain test for 4 days with version 2.01, 170530 firmware, RF modem turned off, 13.49mA Average.
Successfully tested XMIT and GPS commands outside on internal antennas.
